title: Kendall Jenner Is Topless, Flashes Sideboob to Thank Calvin Klein for New Jeans
text:
Comments The 19-year-old model and flashes her sideboob as she bends her body towards her white bed to put the back pocket of her jeans to be the focus of the camera. 
Kendall Jenner went for another racy shot following shower shots with photographer Mert Alas earlier this month. The " Keeping Up with the Kardashians " star took to Instagram on Friday, October 23 to share a black-and-white picture showing her topless in Calvin Klein jeans. The said picture was taken from behind, exposing Kendall's bare back. The 19-year-old model flashed her sideboob as she bent her body towards her white bed to put the back pocket of her jeans to be the focus of the camera. A caption for the picture read, "#mycalvins moment. thanks to @calvinklein for my new jeans. back pocket." Later on the same day, Kendall appeared in a Dubsmash video posted by her younger sister Kylie Jenner . The two had fun mouthing to some lines from Bryson Tiller's song "Don't". At the beginning of the video, they looked sullen. However, as they began lip-syncing, the Jenner sisters were snuggling to each other while sporting their pretty smiles. Video kiriman King Kylie (@kyliejenner) pada Okt 23, 2015 pada 2:37 PDT Kylie also posted another picture of her striking a pose in Kendall's bedroom. The 18-year-old reality TV star looked pretty showing bob hair and pink manicures. She wore gray hat and brown long-sleeved shirt. White bed similar to the one in Kendall's racy picture could be seen in the background. Kylie captioned it, "Kendall's House." Foto kiriman King Kylie (@kyliejenner) pada Okt 23, 2015 pada 1:50 PDT The two are now living separately. Kendall has her own condo in Los Angeles while Kylie has a mansion in an exclusive gated community in Calabasas. Kendall bought her own condo last year while Kylie bought her mansion earlier this year when she was just 17.
